                    onerror="this.src='/images/graphics/console-windows.png'"]
          .slide#slide--build-packages
            p.slide--subtext
              | From your plan &amp; config files, Habitat will <br/>
                generate a complete package.
            .row
              .columns.large-4
                ul.slide--blurbs
                  li.slide--blurb
                    h4 Configurable at runtime
                    p Packages expose the app's tunables
                  li.slide--blurb
                    h4 Aware of their environments
                    p Packages can establish trust<br>relationships between peers
                  li.slide--blurb
                    h4 Can update themselves
                    p Packages can auto-update according to policy
                  li.slide--blurb
                    h4 Ready to communicate
                    p
                      | The HTTP API means packages can express state, be monitored,
