  .production-wrap
    .row
      .production--blurb.columns.medium-6
        h2 How does it work?
        p
          | Habitat is unapologetically app-centric. It's designed with best
            practices for the modern application in mind.
        p
          | Habitat gives you a packaging format and a runtime supervisor
            with deployment coordination and service discovery built in.
        p
          | Habitat packages contain everything the app needs to run with no
            outside dependencies. They are isolated, immutable, and auditable.
        p
          | The Habitat supervisor knows the packaged app's peer relationships,
            upgrade strategy, and policies for restart and security. The
            supervisor is also responsible for runtime configuration and
            connecting to management services, such as monitoring.
        a.button.cta href="/tutorials" Learn Habitat
        p.cta-subtext Our tutorials will get you started fast.
      .production--graphic.columns.medium-6
        img[src="/images/graphics/production.svg" onerror="this.src='/images/graphics/production.png'" alt=""]
